  "texts": [
    "The intelligent human-computer interaction interfaceconnects the physical and digital worlds.",
    "It transfers the sensed multi-source and multi-modal data from the physical world to the digital world, providing support for HDT modeling in the digital world.",
    "Moreover, when the state of people (e.g., emotion, psychology, and behavior) in the physical world changes, the real-time data is also fed back to the digital world to optimize and modify the HDT model. 4.",
    "After receiving the data, the virtual world processes the data, selects features, and stores the processed current and historical data in the HDT database. 5.",
    "HDT uses modeling technology (e.g., ML, DL and continuous learning) and the data in the database to build the HDT model corresponding to the human in the physical world."
  ],
